<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards are enacted pursuant to Paragraph 1 of Article 10 of the Charges and Fees Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fees for the Nationality Permit Certificate and the Nationality Certificate granted and issued by the Ministry of the Interior are charged as follows:
1. Permit Certificate of Naturalization: NT$ 1,200 each.
2. Permit Certificate of Nationality Loss: NT$ 1,200 each.
3. Permit Certificate of Nationality Restoration: NT$ 1,200 each.
4. ROC Nationality Certificate: NT$ 1,000 each.
For those who apply abroad for the proof of loss of nationality or the Nationality Certificate, the fees for the Permit Certificate of Nationality Loss indicated in the preceding paragraph are charged at USD 47 each or USD 60 each by clean bill; as regards payment for those who make the application in Japan, the fees are charged at JPY 5,500 each or JPY 6,300 each by clean bill. The fees for the Nationality Certificate are charged at USD 41 each or USD 53 each by clean bill; and for those who make the application in Japan, the fees are charged at JPY 4,700 each or JPY 5,500 each by clean bill.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[If the Nationality Permit Certificate is tainted, damaged, destroyed or lost, the applicant may apply to the Ministry of the Interior for a renewal or re-issuance at NTD 1,000 each. For those who make the application abroad, the fees for the renewal or re-issuance are charged at USD 41 each or USD 53 each by clean bill; as regards payment for those who make the application in Japan, the fees for the renewal or re-issuance are charged at JPY 4,700 each or JPY 5,500 each by clean bill.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fees for the Nationality Permit Certificate and the Nationality Certificate are collected by the competent authority, which accepts the application for naturalization, loss of nationality, restoration of nationality or the Nationality Certificate and thereafter hands it over, level by level, to the Ministry of the Interior, which will then pay it to the treasury.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Standards are enforced from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
